name: Heyday
summary: Gather GVL, the anchor tenants of HeyDay, offer a glimpse into the upcoming creative space designed specifically for adults with special needs. Marshalltown Times Republican reports on the launch of 'Club Heyday,' a new initiative providing opportunities for these individuals. Forbes shares hints and answers for the latest "Connections" puzzle in the New York Times, published on May 23. Variety explores the upcoming docuseries "Lolla: The Story of Lollapalooza," celebrating the iconic alternative rock festival's 1990s heyday while highlighting Perry Farrell's vision for its future. Lifehacker provides the solution to the NYT "Connections" puzzle published on May 23, 2024. Upstate Business Journal reports on the creators of Hendough expanding their operations to the former Oak Hill Cafe, offering sandwiches and cocktails. Newsweek offers hints and answers for the NYT "Connections" puzzle #347. Eater Portland announces the continued operation of the Food Cart Pod at Portland State University. Rock Paper Shotgun provides hints and answers for the NYT "Connections" puzzle published on May 23. Finally, Yahoo Movies Canada reveals that Ray Winstone will narrate a feature documentary about the heyday of British stunt performers in Hollywood.
